sys_remote_update_set.description:
A toolkit for every ServiceNow developer. Find more at www.sndeveloper.com.
### Version 4.1 * Automatically blacklist illegal fields. * Add prototype property to function explanations. * Fix cross-origin target frame access issue. * Add support for property driven default blacklist and redlist. * Update info page. * Prevent strings containing XML from being quoted so it formats better. * Move timer to the header for better visibility and reference. * Add code example to regular expression tester. * Added format button to user_data for formatting XML. * Fix submit button spinner. * Add support for function prototypes. * Added node log support.
sys_remote_update_set.name: SND Xplore - 4.1
